{"tid":2326622,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"夢想唔可以當飯食","createTime":"2020-12-15T12:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T14:41:48.000Z","uid":105864,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad830b857da3b030e7d420c533b51c325ac3a36","tid":2326622,"uid":105864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:23:49.000Z","msg":"做緊細個寫《我的志願》嘅工<br />\n啲人成日話唔可以做成世，我冇信<br />\n惡法出台後，行業前景急劇惡化<br />\n我仲好中意自己做緊嘅<br />\n但工作環境同前（錢）景<br />\n我知我要快啲轉行<br />\n不過我唔知自己仲可以做咩<br />\n原來夢想唔可以當飯食<br />\n發過夢就好"},{"pid":"82c1751cb79137c5a2485bb21b1c038f41f2f9e8","tid":2326622,"uid":16372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"人冇事先做到世界冠軍"},{"pid":"0fa594e619c81e055da53521c964cd012d4ae863","tid":2326622,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:40:12.000Z","msg":"你個夢想搵到錢咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36424b0d0ad7f6dde9112c8f704bf81a2d2f05db","tid":2326622,"uid":194120,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T13:03:50.000Z","msg":"真人真事，一個40幾歲月入五六皮男人，為完自己自細夢想Quit咗份工返去澳洲喺馬房剷馬屎，佢仲話好難得有呢個機會唔係成日有。"},{"pid":"142c8bd821a32cf0c8834c27c344bcdd140c3487","tid":2326622,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T13:06:55.000Z","msg":"咁起碼你要有飽飯先可以追夢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e596a6d680f29793c1a7d2c0555e333c0915e1b","tid":2326622,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36424b0d0ad7f6dde9112c8f704bf81a2d2f05db","tid":2326622,"uid":194120,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T13:03:50.000Z","msg":"真人真事，一個40幾歲月入五六皮男人，為完自己自細夢想Quit咗份工返去澳洲喺馬房剷馬屎，佢仲話好難得有呢個機會唔係成日有。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"佢既夢想係玩屎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92b5c19d615530035a0b5762d5bab69225f911f","tid":2326622,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislik